column1: The rock band jefferson airplane is playing
One pill makes you larger
And one pill makes you small
Mother is giving Alice a pill
There is Alice in Wonderland. She is ten feet tall
Alice in Wonderland is chasing a rabbit
The girl is falling through a hole
a hookah smoking caterpillar, a caterpillar smoking a shisha
the caterpillar is calling with the phone
Alice in wonderland is becoming small
Men are standing on a chessboard. A knight is standing on a chessboard.
The knight is lifting his arm. The knight is giving directions.
The girl is eating a mushroom. There is a weird kind of mushroom.
The girl is thinking really slow.
Alice in Wonderland
When logic and proportion have fallen sloppy dead
The white knight is talking backward
The red queen. The red queen is off with her head.
There is a dormouse. A kind of mouse.
Feed your head, feed your head, feed your head
Alice in Wonderland
